name: Ritz Classic-Patto

reviews.review_text: Visited Ritz Classic in Goa. The food was just okay, nothing special. Some dishes were decent, but overall it didn't meet my expectations. The service was fine, but the flavors could definitely improve. It’s a good spot for a casual meal, but don’t expect anything extraordinary.

Awesome food, mainly Goan food.

A little bit on the expensive side, however the food is on spot and would love to go again.

Service was done well.

Atmosphere wise, there were few house flies which can be and needs to be prevented.

Everything was nice, the food was great and the ambience was good.

Ordered a Burnt Garlic Prawns Fried Rice, enjoyed it good. But I had a problem with the Caramel Pudding, when served it was bitter in taste so the captain changed it but the replacement was also bitter, I guess due to burnt caramel or old pudding.

I didn't enjoy that, but everything else was good.

description:
### Discovering Ritz Classic-Patto: A Culinary Gem in Caranzalem

Nestled in the vibrant locales of Caranzalem, Ritz Classic-Patto has earned a commendable overall rating of 4 stars from approximately 7,600 reviews. This intimate establishment stands out with its traditional Goan cuisine, prominently featuring specialties like thali (476 mentions) and fish curry (54 mentions), appealing to both locals and tourists seeking an authentic culinary experience.

### Ambiance & Design

Upon entering Ritz Classic-Patto, guests are welcomed into a cozy, casual environment that radiates warmth. The décor reflects a mix of traditional Goan elements and contemporary touches, with wooden furnishings and vibrant wall art depicting coastal life. The atmosphere is generally inviting, though some reviews have noted occasional disturbances from flies, highlighting an area for potential improvement. Based on the visuals from customer photos, the space is accentuated by tasteful lighting, creating a relaxed dining backdrop for both families and groups of friends. 

![Ambiance](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdmCtZfhArk5T6QdXOubalE9BmfjdChz6FjRk0HZ_dtgQH01h12Op0V7Jsd-sWFX-ZNX9cnAFJLoO3Xkb14S84-BXc7H4Bqb-IIvAgjKqWlUAyvT4EbLBMiCqLf8yidUASSmDfTl=w375-h281-p)

### Menu & Culinary Experience

The menu at Ritz Classic-Patto primarily showcases Goan dishes, and it is evident that thali is a standout feature, popular among diners. One customer highlighted their delight with the Burnt Garlic Prawns Fried Rice, suggesting that seafood lovers will find much to enjoy here. However, it is worth noting that individual experiences with some desserts, such as the Caramel Pudding, have varied; one reviewer experienced bitterness in both the original and replacement servings, indicating some inconsistencies in dessert preparation. 

Overall, the presentation is described as appealing, with colorful dishes that bring an inviting aesthetic to the table. Dietary considerations seem to be addressed in portions of the menu, making it a favorable choice for various palates.

![Food Presentation](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdks0R6Wuj_u2vqsZBxAW--pBphSUzwqz_qOrGyVAODCwJHOcq5TuFJl5awswAhH3x_rVCEVLxDEGyXSmyHc0kzavPkqjGBy-_GtFRyPPzDTnP7UmK_T7YrzxbPptBfGHTR1hihb=w375-h281-p)

### Customer Experience & Service

Diners consistently praise the courteous service at Ritz Classic-Patto. While most reviews acknowledge the staff's friendliness and efficiency, there are mentions of the dining experience being slightly marred by pests at times, indicating a need for enhanced cleanliness measures. Customers can expect attentive service during their visit, whether they choose to reserve a table or opt for a walk-in experience, although it might be wise to book ahead during peak times to avoid disappointment.

### Popularity & Reviews

Ritz Classic-Patto enjoys a robust reputation, regularly featured in discussions both online and offline. Many diners express their intent to return, highlighting that, despite some minor drawbacks, the quality of the food makes the visit worthwhile. Social media buzz suggests a solidly established following, especially among those seeking quality Goan cuisine. 

![Customer Food](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdkVLzFhINTBS6uv89zBpx82bjwHF8ZcoaOXTYdOpRnV7e_bt-d4rqGDq0fRkORtVsGtHUMkTn82naj2WsCRHOzzX9Wq3tvWvLVjLTexTprD6qND9IM1jAiVTOsKRuWw4vKUBpUk=w375-h563-p)

### Conclusion

In conclusion, while Ritz Classic-Patto may have room for improvement, particularly with desserts and pest control, the overall offering—especially its Goan thali, seafood, and welcoming atmosphere—strikes a positive chord with many guests. For those in Caranzalem looking for a solid meal in an inviting setting, this restaurant remains a notable contender in Goa’s bustling culinary scene.
